Is anyone there?

116
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:16,240
Help!

117
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,720
Auntie!

118
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:25,120
What are you doing here?

119
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:26,559
What am I doing?

120
00:10:26,559 --> 00:10:30,520
I want to know why you betrayed Yancheng and had an affair,

121
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:33,720
