122
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:38,000
Over those years, we helped you so much.

123
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:40,080
Yet, you dare to have an affair with someone else.

124
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:42,600
You even got pregnant with an illegitimate child.

125
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:45,240
Do you think all of us in the Fu family are dead?

126
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:47,879
No, I didn't. Let me explain, Auntie.

127
00:10:47,879 --> 00:10:49,279
- I didn't. 
 - Don't try to make excuses.

128
00:10:49,279 --> 00:10:52,599
- I'm telling you. No matter how persuasive your words are, 
 - I didn't...

129
00:10:52,599 --> 00:10:56,620
Today, you must get rid of that illegitimate child in your belly.

130
00:10:56,620 --> 00:10:58,000
Do it!

131
00:10:58,000 --> 00:10:59,479
No.

132
